WEBVTT

00:15.460 --> 00:19.960
♪During the dark night♪

00:20.100 --> 00:22.750
♪A guiding light♪

00:23.260 --> 00:25.050
♪Just like you♪

00:25.460 --> 00:29.750
♪Makes life turn bright♪

00:30.330 --> 00:35.180
♪Breaking free from darkness♪

00:35.400 --> 00:38.880
♪You gave me strength♪

00:39.230 --> 00:41.780
♪Running for truth♪

00:41.800 --> 00:45.850
♪I find my path♪

00:46.600 --> 00:50.580
♪Drawing on the hope♪

00:51.200 --> 00:54.580
♪That you render me♪

00:55.130 --> 00:58.010
♪In this long journey♪

00:58.260 --> 01:01.680
♪I run on lightly♪

01:19.180 --> 01:22.980
[Reborn]
[Adapted from Qiang Yu's work, Reborn]

01:22.980 --> 01:24.460
Your uncle wants me to check on her

01:24.460 --> 01:25.620
so that he can feel more at ease.

01:25.810 --> 01:28.140
He doesn't want her to have an episode
and run out to cause trouble again.

01:29.380 --> 01:31.460
By the way, ask your uncle

01:31.460 --> 01:32.620
to keep an eye on her.

01:33.220 --> 01:34.650
Don't let her get worked up again.

01:36.460 --> 01:37.300
Ms. Xiuzhen.

01:37.620 --> 01:39.650
You are the health worker
at the village health clinic?

01:39.650 --> 01:40.170
Yes.

01:40.170 --> 01:41.370
I've worked here for more than 20 years.

01:41.620 --> 01:43.490
I know the illnesses and minor ailments

01:43.490 --> 01:44.210
that everyone has in this village.

01:45.009 --> 01:46.900
Do you know about Qiao Beiyu?

01:49.530 --> 01:50.370
As for Beiyu,

01:50.810 --> 01:52.530
I've definitely heard

01:52.620 --> 01:54.050
what they said about her.

01:54.210 --> 01:56.330
But I don't know for sure
if she had that disease

01:56.330 --> 01:57.500
or not.

01:59.370 --> 02:00.370
But there's something

02:01.410 --> 02:02.820
I remember very clearly.

02:08.330 --> 02:10.270
As soon as Beiyu returned
from Huanzhou Art School

02:10.270 --> 02:11.050
for the winter vacation

02:11.050 --> 02:13.370
she had a miscarriage
and came to the health clinic.

02:14.730 --> 02:17.220
Not long after that, your mom came.

02:18.540 --> 02:19.540
Fanghao.

02:21.450 --> 02:22.220
Mom.

02:25.900 --> 02:26.370
Mom.

02:40.850 --> 02:42.050
A young girl in her early twenties

02:42.329 --> 02:43.690
had a miscarriage.

02:43.770 --> 02:44.410
It was such a shame.

02:44.900 --> 02:45.770
It wasn't the medical staff

02:45.770 --> 02:47.460
who spread the news.

02:47.980 --> 02:50.690
Bad news travels far.

02:51.180 --> 02:52.660
Anyway, Bei had done wrong.

02:52.980 --> 02:55.020
She had this misfortune
at such a young age,

02:55.020 --> 02:56.490
but she didn't learn from the lesson.

02:57.490 --> 03:00.050
She just gave up on herself.

03:00.980 --> 03:02.930
Do you know who the man was?

03:03.260 --> 03:05.210
I don't.

03:05.740 --> 03:07.540
But considering her behavior afterward,

03:08.620 --> 03:10.330
it's not hard to guess.

03:10.620 --> 03:13.290
You can't really blame others
for gossiping.

03:14.620 --> 03:15.490
I got to go.

03:20.079 --> 03:24.980
[Episode 4]
[Lies or Truth]

03:26.750 --> 03:28.400
[Ming Qiuxin: If you're free today,]

03:28.400 --> 03:30.000
[come to the hospital and wait for me.]

03:30.000 --> 03:31.780
[Let's have a meal together.]

03:42.890 --> 03:43.500
What a coincidence.

03:44.690 --> 03:47.060
A major surgery was canceled
at the last minute,

03:48.570 --> 03:50.260
so I have a few hours to rest.

03:50.570 --> 03:53.290
We can grab something together.

03:56.340 --> 03:58.290
Do you still remember
what I like to eat?

03:58.380 --> 04:00.060
You've liked pizza since you were a kid.

04:00.980 --> 04:03.290
There's a new pizza place
in front of the hospital.

04:03.660 --> 04:04.690
Let's try it.

04:05.290 --> 04:06.940
I used to like pizza

04:07.730 --> 04:09.540
when I was six or seven.

04:10.890 --> 04:12.570
I'm 17 now.

04:12.980 --> 04:14.380
After Mom left,

04:14.850 --> 04:16.339
I never ate pizza anymore.

04:17.060 --> 04:17.660
It was you

04:18.820 --> 04:20.450
who made Mom leave me.

04:22.100 --> 04:23.410
Even before Grandpa died,

04:23.410 --> 04:24.690
you didn't tell me.

04:27.570 --> 04:28.930
You were preparing

04:28.930 --> 04:30.100
for the senior high school
entrance exam.

04:31.570 --> 04:32.730
I didn't want to distract you.

04:39.540 --> 04:40.730
Did that exam matter?

04:41.220 --> 04:42.500
Did the biology competition matter?

04:43.610 --> 04:44.409
Were they more important

04:44.409 --> 04:45.980
than the relationship
between me, Mom, and Grandpa?

04:46.290 --> 04:47.570
It's all in the past.

04:47.570 --> 04:48.409
What's the point of bringing it up?

04:48.409 --> 04:49.220
Come. Let's go eat.

04:52.220 --> 04:53.500
I tried to understand you,

04:54.290 --> 04:55.730
but you've never changed.

04:57.730 --> 04:58.850
Eat it yourself.

05:10.660 --> 05:12.290
All you care about is your patients

05:12.290 --> 05:13.290
and surgeries.

05:13.980 --> 05:14.940
What about me and Sheng?

05:15.220 --> 05:16.380
Have you ever cared about us?

05:16.690 --> 05:17.730
I know

05:17.850 --> 05:19.060
you've sacrificed a lot.

05:19.780 --> 05:21.220
Can you try to understand me?

05:21.220 --> 05:22.220
I did try

05:22.220 --> 05:23.380
to understand you.

05:24.380 --> 05:25.170
But what about you?

05:25.940 --> 05:26.820
Sheng also needs

05:26.820 --> 05:28.690
a father who can spend time with him.

05:29.340 --> 05:29.980
I'm very sorry.

05:29.980 --> 05:30.820
Stop apologizing.

05:32.450 --> 05:34.380
You leave us whenever your phone rings.

05:34.380 --> 05:35.220
Every single time!

05:36.130 --> 05:37.890
Why is it always Sheng and I
who sacrifice

05:37.890 --> 05:40.050
so you can be a good doctor?

05:40.540 --> 05:42.020
I've had enough of this.

05:43.610 --> 05:45.930
Mom, don't go!

05:54.170 --> 05:55.340
Mom!

06:12.460 --> 06:13.290
I'll carry you up there.

06:13.850 --> 06:14.290
Okay.

06:15.370 --> 06:15.930
Be careful.

06:20.290 --> 06:20.930
Good.

06:24.700 --> 06:25.290
Slowly.

06:25.930 --> 06:26.700
Can you stand?

06:27.340 --> 06:27.980
Yes.

06:28.170 --> 06:29.250
Good. Come.

06:31.370 --> 06:32.220
Hold onto me.

06:32.540 --> 06:33.140
Don't be afraid.

06:33.140 --> 06:33.700
Be steady.

06:34.730 --> 06:35.900
Sheng, listen.

06:36.460 --> 06:37.409
What is it?

06:39.050 --> 06:40.340
The rustling leaves in the wind.

06:43.610 --> 06:46.050
And the singing birds.

06:47.930 --> 06:48.810
Sheng, look.

06:50.460 --> 06:51.370
There's a bird.

06:52.930 --> 06:53.930
It's flying past.

06:54.700 --> 06:56.659
The waves of the river.

06:56.900 --> 06:57.780
Did you hear that?

06:58.580 --> 07:00.020
When you're upset,

07:00.020 --> 07:01.730
try to listen to the sound of nature.

07:01.900 --> 07:03.290
They're magical.

07:04.250 --> 07:05.140
Listening to it

07:05.140 --> 07:07.700
makes you feel calm

07:07.780 --> 07:10.100
and forget about all those worries.

07:10.100 --> 07:10.810
All right?

07:10.810 --> 07:11.490
Yes.

07:12.050 --> 07:12.850
Give it a try.

07:31.980 --> 07:33.700
Hello, is this Ming Sheng?

07:34.460 --> 07:35.250
Hello?

07:36.409 --> 07:38.020
I'd like to talk to my mom.

07:38.810 --> 07:39.610
I'm sorry.

07:39.700 --> 07:41.290
Anna is in the recording studio
right now.

07:41.370 --> 07:42.250
If it's urgent,

07:42.250 --> 07:43.490
I'll tell her once she's done.

07:44.170 --> 07:44.980
It's fine.

07:45.409 --> 07:46.250
Never mind.

08:04.980 --> 08:06.370
[Sheng]
Have you checked your mail?

08:09.680 --> 08:11.200
[Huanzhou People's Hospital.
Qiao Beiyu's EMR]

08:14.680 --> 08:17.000
[Report of HIV Antibody
Confirmatory Testing]

08:17.000 --> 08:18.250
[Qiao Beiyu]

08:20.350 --> 08:23.780
[Positive]

08:24.410 --> 08:25.540
I've contacted them.

08:25.540 --> 08:27.460
The hospital will mail it to you later.

08:27.460 --> 08:29.170
Please watch your mail.

08:31.410 --> 08:32.220
Sometimes

08:32.700 --> 08:34.980
we try so hard to find the answer.

08:35.929 --> 08:37.539
But when we finally find it,

08:38.100 --> 08:39.539
even though it's resolved,

08:40.140 --> 08:41.370
it also means

08:41.490 --> 08:43.370
all our previous efforts
have been in vain.

08:46.850 --> 08:47.930
It's been incredibly rainy this year.

08:48.780 --> 08:49.780
The fruit trees are drowning,

08:49.780 --> 08:50.660
and the patch is dead.

08:51.460 --> 08:53.100
If we don't spray pesticides
to drive out pests,

08:54.050 --> 08:54.810
there won't be a harvest.

08:54.810 --> 08:55.490
Qingyu.

08:55.580 --> 08:57.580
Isn't that Uncle Haisheng's patch?

08:57.580 --> 08:59.540
They treat us like free labor.

09:01.490 --> 09:03.020
Why isn't she back yet?

09:03.930 --> 09:05.540
We're family.

09:05.540 --> 09:06.930
You shouldn't have said that.

09:07.100 --> 09:08.020
Besides,

09:08.490 --> 09:10.410
haven't you eaten any fruit
planted by your Uncle Haisheng?

09:10.780 --> 09:11.980
Don't rest your legs here.

09:11.980 --> 09:13.850
He used to be the village secretary.

09:13.850 --> 09:15.340
He lost his job.

09:16.250 --> 09:18.810
I can't even lift my legs.

09:18.810 --> 09:20.490
I'm going to rest at home
for a few days.

09:21.780 --> 09:23.810
Put your legs down. This is rude.

09:23.810 --> 09:24.810
Jiangsheng, have some water.

09:25.490 --> 09:26.410
I'm good.

09:26.700 --> 09:27.610
I want some.

09:28.170 --> 09:28.980
Me too.

09:40.410 --> 09:41.220
Look who's home.

09:41.250 --> 09:42.050
It's already late.

09:42.050 --> 09:43.170
Why are you back so late?

09:44.220 --> 09:45.610
I went to the study room.

09:46.730 --> 09:47.580
Why didn't you keep an eye on the time?

09:47.580 --> 09:48.660
It's already late at night.

09:49.660 --> 09:51.220
I lost track of time.

09:51.580 --> 09:53.460
It's a good thing Qing likes studying.

09:53.460 --> 09:54.660
They say students
of Huanzhou High School

09:54.700 --> 09:56.370
are bound to get into top universities.

09:56.730 --> 09:58.130
You have a bright future ahead of you.

09:58.580 --> 09:59.580
I'll go back to my room.

10:00.100 --> 10:01.370
Me too.

10:03.180 --> 10:03.700
Qingyu.

10:06.130 --> 10:07.100
I'm serious.

10:08.490 --> 10:09.530
It's late

10:09.700 --> 10:10.850
and dark outside.

10:10.980 --> 10:12.890
What if you ran into bad guys?

10:13.460 --> 10:14.130
Girls don't come home

10:14.130 --> 10:15.490
this late at night.

10:15.700 --> 10:16.700
You were worrying me.

10:17.650 --> 10:18.420
All right.

10:18.420 --> 10:19.580
I won't do this again.

10:19.580 --> 10:20.610
Do remember well.

10:21.010 --> 10:22.250
Didn't she say

10:22.250 --> 10:23.490
she lost track of time?

10:23.650 --> 10:24.890
She didn't do it on purpose.

10:26.370 --> 10:27.300
Go to sleep now.

10:31.490 --> 10:32.010
Wait.

10:32.530 --> 10:34.340
Why doesn't Qingyu have to work?

10:34.340 --> 10:35.940
She's the only one who relaxes.

10:35.940 --> 10:37.250
I want to go to the study room, too.

10:37.890 --> 10:38.730
What for?

10:38.730 --> 10:39.370
Reading.

10:40.250 --> 10:41.940
Do you mean gaming?

10:47.130 --> 10:48.010
You're so unfair!

10:59.370 --> 11:00.180
Yu.

11:01.340 --> 11:03.890
I finally knew why Dad and Mom
never cleared up the rumors

11:03.890 --> 11:05.370
about Qiao Beiyu's death.

11:06.770 --> 11:07.580
Why?

11:07.770 --> 11:10.250
Because the rumors are the truth.

11:10.580 --> 11:11.220
What?

11:11.980 --> 11:14.850
Are you saying that she died of AIDS?

11:15.180 --> 11:17.420
Even though I didn't want to admit it,

11:17.730 --> 11:19.100
deep down,

11:19.100 --> 11:21.100
I always felt something was off

11:21.100 --> 11:22.100
about the cause of her death,

11:22.940 --> 11:25.010
because unless she really had
that kind of disease,

11:25.340 --> 11:28.370
the way Dad, Mom,
her friends, and family reacted

11:28.370 --> 11:29.610
won't make sense.

11:31.220 --> 11:33.340
But because Mom and Dad kept denying it,

11:33.940 --> 11:36.850
I thought there was some hidden truth
behind her death.

11:37.730 --> 11:39.700
I always wanted to clear her name,

11:40.010 --> 11:41.340
but it was all in vain.

11:41.490 --> 11:42.820
What proof did you find?

11:42.820 --> 11:44.460
Her medical record was left
in People's Hospital.

11:44.940 --> 11:46.420
It's true she had that kind of disease,

11:46.420 --> 11:47.340
like everyone said.

11:47.940 --> 11:51.700
We still have to bear all the gossip.

11:52.370 --> 11:52.770
What?

11:52.770 --> 11:54.850
So the rumors are true?

11:55.820 --> 11:56.530
Plus,

11:57.130 --> 11:59.420
she had a miscarriage
in Nanqiao Village.

12:00.650 --> 12:01.370
Really?

12:02.980 --> 12:04.100
How did you know?

12:04.100 --> 12:05.420
I met Ms. Xiuzhen earlier today.

12:05.420 --> 12:06.770
She told me about that.

12:07.060 --> 12:07.820
Could it be

12:08.850 --> 12:11.370
this guy who caused her death?

12:11.770 --> 12:13.490
Don't say things without proof.

12:15.370 --> 12:19.340
I must find out who he is.

12:31.340 --> 12:31.980
Mumu.

12:34.530 --> 12:35.530
Please do me a favor.

12:37.300 --> 12:39.420
Pass this on to Ming Sheng.

12:39.890 --> 12:40.890
But remember

12:40.890 --> 12:41.610
not to tell him

12:41.610 --> 12:43.340
it's from me.

12:46.180 --> 12:47.010
Don't worry.

12:47.130 --> 12:48.340
All right. Thank you.

12:48.890 --> 12:49.420
See you.

13:02.130 --> 13:03.220
Nice shot.

13:03.340 --> 13:04.180
Pass the ball.

13:04.180 --> 13:04.420
Come.

13:06.250 --> 13:07.010
Look!

13:07.980 --> 13:08.700
He's handsome, right?

13:08.700 --> 13:09.460
Yeah.

13:09.530 --> 13:11.420
He looks great.

13:11.890 --> 13:13.250
I'm making it my desktop background.

13:14.700 --> 13:15.490
Sheng.

13:16.890 --> 13:17.700
You guys go ahead.

13:18.370 --> 13:19.490
I'll take a break.

13:19.700 --> 13:20.850
I'm taking a break.

13:26.730 --> 13:29.180
Sch, they know each other too?

13:30.980 --> 13:32.060
I can sense some jealousy.

13:32.490 --> 13:33.420
What do you mean?

13:34.180 --> 13:35.130
It's more like a sour taste.

13:35.130 --> 13:35.980
Nice.

13:36.340 --> 13:38.530
Mumu is pretty

13:38.530 --> 13:39.340
and intelligent.

13:40.060 --> 13:41.420
What are they talking about?

13:42.940 --> 13:43.980
Compared to her,

13:44.010 --> 13:45.490
we're just sidekicks.

13:46.490 --> 13:47.490
You are,

13:47.820 --> 13:48.610
but I'm not.

13:51.770 --> 13:52.650
I have a scoop.

13:52.700 --> 13:53.490
Are you interested?

13:54.010 --> 13:54.650
What's it about?

13:54.650 --> 13:55.420
Shoot.

13:56.650 --> 13:58.220
I'll buy you drinks for the entire week.

14:01.060 --> 14:03.130
It is said
that Ming Sheng and Wang Mumu

14:03.460 --> 14:04.890
have been good friends

14:04.890 --> 14:06.130
since childhood.

14:06.250 --> 14:07.300
Did you know
"Romance of the Three Kingdoms"?

14:07.300 --> 14:08.220
Oath of the Peach Garden.

14:08.610 --> 14:09.890
They are sworn siblings.

14:09.980 --> 14:11.130
Their relationship is simple and pure.

14:11.300 --> 14:12.490
Oath of the Peach Garden?

14:13.300 --> 14:14.730
Isn't that about three guys?

14:14.850 --> 14:15.460
She's a girl.

14:17.220 --> 14:17.890
Oh, come on.

14:17.980 --> 14:20.180
This is a metaphor.

14:22.250 --> 14:22.850
Whatever.

15:04.530 --> 15:05.060
Over here.

15:05.610 --> 15:07.220
Have you been waiting long?

15:07.220 --> 15:07.610
No, not at all.

15:07.610 --> 15:08.420
I just arrived.

15:09.420 --> 15:10.420
Pay no mind to them.

15:14.700 --> 15:15.850
I bought you bubble tea.

15:16.220 --> 15:17.060
Thanks.

15:18.980 --> 15:19.610
Oh, right.

15:20.770 --> 15:22.890
I don't quite understand
this essay topic.

15:24.060 --> 15:25.130
It's...

15:25.370 --> 15:28.460
[White Lie]
What's your opinion of white lies?

15:30.530 --> 15:31.890
A lie is a lie.

15:32.220 --> 15:34.010
Even if when wrapped in kindness,

15:34.180 --> 15:35.650
its nature doesn't change.

15:35.850 --> 15:36.850
But white lies

15:36.850 --> 15:38.300
are meant well for the sake of people.

15:38.770 --> 15:40.850
That's just something
people impose on others.

15:41.180 --> 15:42.980
This so-called kindness

15:43.130 --> 15:44.770
often causes great harm.

15:45.460 --> 15:46.700
Does the truth

15:47.610 --> 15:48.850
really matter to you?

15:54.610 --> 15:55.770
Have you ever thought

15:55.850 --> 15:58.010
that the truth can be cruel

15:58.770 --> 15:59.940
and unacceptable?

16:04.650 --> 16:05.530
I can accept it,

16:05.700 --> 16:07.610
and I will bear all the consequences.

16:10.490 --> 16:11.580
Maybe it's different for everyone.

16:12.700 --> 16:13.300
There's another topic.

16:22.700 --> 16:23.490
Qiao Qingyu.

16:24.060 --> 16:24.650
Mom.

16:25.610 --> 16:26.340
Come home with me.

16:26.340 --> 16:27.060
Hello, madam.

16:27.060 --> 16:27.650
I'm Qingyu's...

16:27.650 --> 16:28.530
I don't care who you are.

16:28.650 --> 16:29.700
Just stay away from her.

16:30.250 --> 16:30.730
Let's go.

16:32.010 --> 16:32.770
Qingyu...

16:33.250 --> 16:34.060
Madam.

16:35.130 --> 16:35.940
Madam.

16:36.820 --> 16:37.580
Qingyu.

16:57.770 --> 16:58.650
It tastes good.

16:59.770 --> 17:01.820
Here you go. Your favorite flavor.

17:10.420 --> 17:11.849
To be honest, I can't really cook.

17:11.849 --> 17:13.130
Grandpa taught me that.

17:22.420 --> 17:23.980
Today's Mid-Autumn Festival.

17:24.890 --> 17:26.180
When Grandpa was still around,

17:26.730 --> 17:28.460
he'd definitely celebrate it with us.

17:32.650 --> 17:33.460
When I was a kid,

17:35.220 --> 17:36.730
he used to take me to buy this.

17:38.490 --> 17:40.300
He made mooncakes
with salted egg yolk filling.

17:41.340 --> 17:42.940
He knew where to find the best lanterns.

17:45.460 --> 17:46.370
But now,

17:47.820 --> 17:48.460
he's gone.

17:51.530 --> 17:53.180
Even if Grandpa has gone,
I'm still here.

18:04.650 --> 18:06.420
Here's from a friend of mine.

18:06.530 --> 18:07.770
Since you like basketball,

18:07.820 --> 18:09.490
I'll give it to you.

18:10.530 --> 18:11.890
Lucky me.

18:25.610 --> 18:26.580
Is your friend

18:28.330 --> 18:29.330
Ming Qiuxin?

18:33.010 --> 18:34.250
Mr. Ming's stuff

18:34.250 --> 18:36.570
always smells like disinfectant.

18:42.660 --> 18:44.660
You haven't made up with Mr. Ming yet?

18:51.220 --> 18:54.010
Grandpa was already severely ill,

18:54.330 --> 18:55.620
and he was barely alive,

18:55.620 --> 18:58.090
depending on the ventilator.

18:58.290 --> 19:00.730
Mr. Ming is the best surgeon
in the province.

19:01.220 --> 19:02.860
Even though treatments
were discontinued,

19:02.980 --> 19:04.900
I believe he made the best choice

19:04.900 --> 19:06.420
for Grandpa.

19:06.420 --> 19:07.700
That's two different things.

19:09.530 --> 19:11.220
I know he's skilled,

19:11.620 --> 19:12.530
but I hate him.

19:13.090 --> 19:14.220
Why?

19:14.810 --> 19:16.730
Because he didn't give Grandpa a chance
to choose.

19:17.140 --> 19:19.090
He decided Grandpa's fate
without asking.

19:19.220 --> 19:19.980
As for me,

19:21.050 --> 19:22.460
I didn't even have the right to know.

19:28.250 --> 19:29.420
Perhaps he thought
he was making the best choice

19:29.420 --> 19:30.700
for Grandpa and you.

19:31.250 --> 19:33.050
That's his perspective.

19:33.050 --> 19:34.180
He thought he was doing it for my sake,

19:34.180 --> 19:35.570
but, in fact, he didn't.

19:38.940 --> 19:40.250
Return this to him.

19:40.860 --> 19:42.460
I won't accept his fake kindness.

19:43.250 --> 19:44.050
One day,

19:45.010 --> 19:46.050
I'll leave this home

19:47.220 --> 19:48.530
and completely get rid of him.

20:03.900 --> 20:05.860
Didn't you go to the study room?

20:06.380 --> 20:07.810
I was going there to study.

20:07.900 --> 20:10.180
I just happened to run into Ma Mingkai.

20:10.180 --> 20:10.940
Happened to?

20:11.570 --> 20:12.700
That's too much of a coincidence.

20:15.140 --> 20:16.980
I noticed you had been
acting strangely these days.

20:17.250 --> 20:18.980
Were you with him last night?

20:18.980 --> 20:19.620
No.

20:19.810 --> 20:21.140
Qingyu, are you still denying it?

20:22.290 --> 20:23.620
I asked the study room staff.

20:24.010 --> 20:25.460
You weren't there last night.

20:26.330 --> 20:27.730
We're just classmates.

20:27.730 --> 20:29.090
It's not what you think.

20:29.090 --> 20:30.090
Qiao Qingyu, listen.

20:30.090 --> 20:31.140
What you're saying right now

20:31.140 --> 20:32.860
is exactly what Qiao Beiyu
once said to me.

20:39.330 --> 20:40.050
Reputation matters

20:40.860 --> 20:42.010
more than studying.

20:42.810 --> 20:44.570
Now that you've reached this age,

20:44.570 --> 20:45.570
there are so many temptations out there.

20:46.050 --> 20:47.050
You can't afford to slip up,

20:47.050 --> 20:47.860
understand?

20:48.860 --> 20:50.010
If you fall behind in your studies,
you can always catch up.

20:50.330 --> 20:51.530
But what can you do
if your reputation is ruined?

20:51.530 --> 20:52.420
You can never clear your name.

20:52.420 --> 20:53.460
It'll haunt you
for the rest of your life.

20:53.660 --> 20:55.220
Your sister is the best example.

20:55.620 --> 20:57.250
People won't stop talking about her
even after her death.

20:57.250 --> 20:58.090
Didn't you know that?

21:00.770 --> 21:02.140
Do you want to end up like her?

21:10.330 --> 21:11.290
Starting tomorrow,

21:11.730 --> 21:13.250
you're not allowed
to be alone with boys,

21:13.250 --> 21:14.490
no matter what the situation is.

21:15.330 --> 21:16.180
Understood?

21:18.860 --> 21:19.980
If not, I will have Jinyu
keep an eye on you

21:19.980 --> 21:21.140
no matter where you are.

21:44.180 --> 21:45.530
Why are you sitting here, Qingyu?

22:03.530 --> 22:04.490
Bei?

22:05.900 --> 22:06.490
Come.

22:09.250 --> 22:09.940
Come.

22:10.140 --> 22:10.700
Come.

22:18.620 --> 22:19.180
Bei,

22:19.420 --> 22:20.010
hurry up!

22:20.290 --> 22:20.900
Where to?

22:21.530 --> 22:22.420
Where are we going?

22:22.700 --> 22:24.180
Come. Let's leave this place.

22:24.730 --> 22:25.460
Let's go and find your parents.

22:25.770 --> 22:26.730
Where are we heading to?

22:29.290 --> 22:30.250
It's Wenqiu.

22:31.180 --> 22:31.770
Wenqiu.

22:33.180 --> 22:33.770
Wenqiu!

22:34.660 --> 22:35.250
Wenqiu!

22:36.010 --> 22:36.620
Wenqiu!

22:41.660 --> 22:42.620
You're running around again.

22:43.380 --> 22:43.980
Why are you at it again?

22:44.230 --> 22:45.250
[Beiyu]

22:49.770 --> 22:50.250
Let's go.

22:50.490 --> 22:50.980
Wenqiu,

22:51.330 --> 22:51.940
stop running.

22:52.050 --> 22:52.810
Let's go home for dinner.

22:52.900 --> 22:54.050
Leave me alone.

22:54.180 --> 22:55.050
Qing, go home.

22:55.380 --> 22:55.620
Go.

22:55.620 --> 22:56.090
No.

22:56.380 --> 22:57.570
I won't leave you alone.

22:57.570 --> 22:58.330
Get off.

22:58.620 --> 23:00.010
Let go of me.

23:00.180 --> 23:01.180
Let's go home for dinner.

23:02.490 --> 23:04.140
We'll go pick flowers after that, okay?

23:04.140 --> 23:05.180
We go pick flowers after dinner.

23:06.330 --> 23:06.860
Let's go, Qing.

23:09.530 --> 23:10.090
Let me see.

23:15.940 --> 23:18.010
Should we call Uncle Jiangsheng
to join us?

23:18.860 --> 23:20.050
They just picked their dinner up.

23:20.050 --> 23:20.620
Hurry and eat.

23:20.980 --> 23:21.730
Eat your food.

23:21.730 --> 23:22.250
Mind your own business.

23:24.530 --> 23:25.620
Stop crying.

23:25.810 --> 23:27.140
Hurry and eat up.

23:27.810 --> 23:28.730
You were running around again.

23:28.810 --> 23:31.090
I can't watch you all the time.

23:32.050 --> 23:33.730
I can't manage that alone.

23:35.620 --> 23:37.050
I feel pity for Aunt Qin.

23:38.730 --> 23:40.090
Your uncle is more pitiful.

23:40.570 --> 23:42.250
The one who looks after a patient
is more exhausting,

23:42.980 --> 23:44.180
especially one with such an illness.

23:44.940 --> 23:46.490
He can't spare time
to look after other things.

23:47.180 --> 23:49.290
He has taken her to many doctors.

23:49.420 --> 23:50.730
But over time,

23:50.940 --> 23:52.050
no one can really tolerate it.

23:52.460 --> 23:53.490
You always cry.

23:53.770 --> 23:54.860
What's the point of crying?

23:55.460 --> 23:58.420
I work in the field every day.
Am I not tired?

23:59.140 --> 24:00.620
Still, I have to look around for you.

24:01.090 --> 24:02.010
Stop crying.

24:02.490 --> 24:04.250
Why did you run around?

24:05.220 --> 24:06.770
And you're crying now.

24:07.050 --> 24:09.330
Can't you give me a break?

24:09.900 --> 24:12.220
Stop making me worry, okay?

24:40.250 --> 24:43.550
[Love is the brightest element here.
But it's also the start of a disaster.]

24:45.860 --> 24:47.330
Come. Let's leave this place.

24:47.860 --> 24:48.770
Let's go and find your parents.

24:54.000 --> 24:56.080
[Beiyu]

25:18.770 --> 25:20.570
Jinyu, wake up. Come on.

25:20.570 --> 25:21.530
What?

25:22.180 --> 25:23.050
Get up.

25:39.330 --> 25:40.660
What's wrong with you?

25:40.660 --> 25:42.700
Why are you taking me to the graveyard

25:43.140 --> 25:44.220
in the middle of the night?

25:44.570 --> 25:46.010
I took you here for courage.

25:47.770 --> 25:49.420
I'm gutless.

25:51.050 --> 25:52.700
Are you even a man?

25:55.770 --> 25:56.620
Hold this.

26:02.570 --> 26:03.420
It's raining.

26:03.420 --> 26:04.730
Will it get heavier?

26:14.290 --> 26:15.700
Is this Beiyu's tomb?

26:18.250 --> 26:20.420
I didn't know those in Nanqiao Village
still remembered her.

26:35.250 --> 26:37.090
I thought you hated her.

26:37.660 --> 26:40.010
Why are you here burning joss paper
for her at this hour?

26:42.050 --> 26:43.180
I hated her,

26:44.380 --> 26:45.570
but I also felt sorry for her.

27:04.420 --> 27:06.140
You treasured this photo very much.

27:07.220 --> 27:08.250
Take it with you.

27:48.530 --> 27:49.770
Dad and Mom didn't let us come

27:50.220 --> 27:51.730
when Beiyu was buried.

27:52.810 --> 27:54.330
She was such a beautiful girl.

27:54.460 --> 27:55.330
Yet

27:55.770 --> 27:58.290
she's buried in a shabby place
after death.

28:01.140 --> 28:02.860
Qingyu, isn't that our home?

28:04.010 --> 28:04.940
It's on fire!

28:14.090 --> 28:15.290
I heard there was a fire last night.

28:15.290 --> 28:16.530
Let's go and take a look.

28:16.900 --> 28:19.090
It's so dangerous.

28:20.460 --> 28:22.330
Is it terrible?
Everything is burned down.

28:23.620 --> 28:24.620
Which spot started the fire?

28:24.620 --> 28:26.050
Qin's.

28:26.460 --> 28:27.900
There's a lot of work.

28:31.460 --> 28:34.140
Qiao, your place caught fire last night.

28:34.140 --> 28:34.700
What happened?

28:35.050 --> 28:36.860
It's said Qin left a cigarette burning

28:36.860 --> 28:39.090
last night.

28:39.420 --> 28:41.090
It was that mad woman.

28:41.250 --> 28:42.620
Luckily, they noticed it soon.

28:42.620 --> 28:43.620
Otherwise,

28:43.770 --> 28:45.530
everything would've burnt
to the ground.

28:45.660 --> 28:46.730
This is so dangerous.

28:47.460 --> 28:49.290
Is everyone okay, Qiao?

28:50.530 --> 28:51.330
Yes.

28:52.180 --> 28:54.140
My second brother was taken
to the hospital last night.

28:54.940 --> 28:56.330
Everything has been burned down.

28:56.330 --> 28:59.090
You wouldn't know if he could survive.

28:59.090 --> 29:00.460
Do you need a hand?

29:00.460 --> 29:01.570
No, thanks.

29:01.570 --> 29:02.770
You may leave. Don't gather here.

29:04.490 --> 29:05.980
Stop gathering here.

29:06.620 --> 29:07.620
Go home. Stop gathering here.

29:07.620 --> 29:09.570
We just wanted to help. Let's leave.

29:27.730 --> 29:30.530
Dad, Mom, should we head back now?

29:45.010 --> 29:46.140
I'm in love with him.

29:46.730 --> 29:48.220
He was my first.

29:48.810 --> 29:50.810
I love him.

29:50.810 --> 29:54.050
He's the only one I rely on
in Nanqiao Village.

30:20.250 --> 30:22.730
Dad and Mom can stay more comfortably
in that old house.

30:25.180 --> 30:27.490
We'll gather money.

30:27.490 --> 30:29.620
I'll try to figure something out.

31:03.860 --> 31:04.660
Mom.

31:08.010 --> 31:08.810
Mom.

31:09.940 --> 31:10.940
It's going to rain.

31:31.010 --> 31:32.490
You looked like

31:33.490 --> 31:35.620
a young bird that was about to take off.

31:40.050 --> 31:41.660
Did you grow taller?

31:43.090 --> 31:44.660
I've been this tall since last year.

31:47.220 --> 31:47.570
Hmm.

31:49.900 --> 31:51.140
Let's go. It's raining.

32:13.010 --> 32:14.770
Why is my left eye blurry?

32:16.940 --> 32:17.620
Gosh.

32:22.290 --> 32:24.180
Behave. Mr. Sun is here.

32:24.860 --> 32:26.330
Ming Sheng is looking at you.

32:33.860 --> 32:35.010
He's staring at you.

32:35.660 --> 32:37.330
Turn around. Stop looking at him.

32:54.570 --> 32:55.010
All right.

32:55.490 --> 32:56.140
Next, please.

33:15.700 --> 33:17.330
Excuse me, have you seen my shoes?

33:17.330 --> 33:18.090
No.

33:18.660 --> 33:20.050
Excuse me, have you seen my shoes?

33:20.220 --> 33:21.010
No.

33:22.380 --> 33:22.810
Everyone,

33:23.490 --> 33:24.940
have you seen Qiao Qingyu's shoes?

33:26.940 --> 33:28.180
Qiao Qingyu lost her shoes.

33:36.700 --> 33:37.420
Silence.

33:38.490 --> 33:40.180
Who saw Qiao Qingyu's shoes?

33:40.380 --> 33:41.460
Bring them out.

33:51.620 --> 33:52.420
Everyone,

33:52.770 --> 33:54.620
after the National Day holiday,

33:54.620 --> 33:55.460
Grade 2

33:55.460 --> 33:57.220
has been divided into two streams.

33:57.530 --> 33:59.250
Only a few of you
will go to the art stream,

33:59.250 --> 34:00.810
and the rest will form

34:00.810 --> 34:03.250
the new science stream class as Class 5.

34:03.620 --> 34:04.250
That's good.

34:05.980 --> 34:07.010
Okay, everyone.

34:07.010 --> 34:08.139
Since you're divided
into different streams,

34:08.219 --> 34:09.250
it means

34:09.330 --> 34:11.050
you're one step closer to NCEE.

34:11.290 --> 34:12.489
I really hope

34:12.570 --> 34:14.139
you won't slack off

34:14.179 --> 34:15.250
during this pivotal moment.

34:15.489 --> 34:16.330
Speaking of which,

34:16.380 --> 34:17.900
I know it's cliche,

34:18.179 --> 34:19.489
but I must share this motivational quote

34:19.659 --> 34:21.010
with you all.

34:21.699 --> 34:23.460
"A soldier's battleground
is on the frontline.

34:23.489 --> 34:24.730
A worker's battleground
is in the factory.

34:24.730 --> 34:26.489
What about students'?"

34:26.620 --> 34:28.699
- "In the classroom."
- "In the classroom."

34:29.940 --> 34:30.570
All right.

34:30.570 --> 34:32.380
I know you're sick of hearing that.

34:32.460 --> 34:33.219
I hope

34:33.219 --> 34:35.530
when you receive your report cards
by the end of the term,

34:35.699 --> 34:37.090
the atmosphere will be just as exciting.

34:39.530 --> 34:40.620
Let me repeat this once again.

34:41.219 --> 34:42.090
Pay attention to the attendance.

34:43.250 --> 34:44.050
Don't be late.

34:45.219 --> 34:46.139
Now that you're joining
different streams,

34:46.420 --> 34:47.570
the headmaster
will pay more attention to you.

34:47.570 --> 34:48.330
Do you hear me?

34:48.620 --> 34:49.810
All right.

34:50.940 --> 34:51.770
You're dismissed now.

34:53.770 --> 34:54.570
Thank you, sir!

35:00.530 --> 35:01.090
Sheng.

35:01.730 --> 35:02.180
Sheng,

35:02.380 --> 35:03.180
let's go play basketball.

35:03.220 --> 35:04.330
Okay. You guys go first.

35:04.330 --> 35:06.460
Sure. We'll go grab the spot first.

35:09.860 --> 35:10.700
Are you done?

35:11.010 --> 35:11.940
One moment.

35:13.330 --> 35:14.140
Let's go.

35:14.420 --> 35:15.980
I don't feel like going home.

35:16.620 --> 35:17.250
Neither do I.

35:18.420 --> 35:19.090
It's early now.

35:19.180 --> 35:20.770
How about we try the claw machine?

35:21.140 --> 35:21.730
Let's go.

35:29.220 --> 35:31.210
Throw this for me. You're on duty today.

36:22.130 --> 36:24.090
Sheng, we've been waiting for you.

36:24.530 --> 36:25.340
What are you looking at?

36:26.380 --> 36:27.260
Nothing.

36:28.340 --> 36:29.900
Are you following Qiao Qingyu?

36:29.900 --> 36:31.130
Why would I do that?

36:31.170 --> 36:32.130
I'm not nuts.

36:32.130 --> 36:33.340
Come. Let's go play basketball.

36:33.420 --> 36:33.940
I'm not playing.

36:34.530 --> 36:34.860
Why not?

36:35.380 --> 36:36.780
There's something I need to do.

36:42.490 --> 36:43.780
Why are Qiao Qingyu's shoes

36:43.780 --> 36:45.260
the same as Sheng's?

36:45.490 --> 36:46.980
Could those actually be Sheng's shoes?

36:47.300 --> 36:47.820
Come on.

36:48.130 --> 36:48.650
Let's play now.

36:49.940 --> 36:50.530
All right.

36:50.530 --> 36:52.460
I'm heading back to the shop now.

36:52.570 --> 36:53.210
Okay. Tell him

36:53.210 --> 36:54.300
I'll be back in 20 minutes.

36:54.300 --> 36:55.090
That's it.

36:59.460 --> 37:00.980
Whose shoes are these?

37:01.860 --> 37:03.010
Where are yours?

37:03.820 --> 37:05.010
I lost them.

37:05.130 --> 37:06.860
I found these in a trash can.

37:06.900 --> 37:07.900
You're a grown-up.

37:07.900 --> 37:08.740
How could you possibly
lose your own shoes?

37:08.740 --> 37:09.940
Where did you take them off?

37:11.690 --> 37:12.650
These shoes look just fine.

37:12.650 --> 37:13.980
Why would someone throw them away?

37:16.050 --> 37:16.740
Qiao Qingyu,

37:16.980 --> 37:18.570
you wouldn't find these shoes like that

37:18.650 --> 37:19.980
unless someone wanted you to wear them.

37:20.010 --> 37:20.820
What has happened?

37:20.820 --> 37:21.740
Why are you wearing a guy's shoes

37:21.740 --> 37:23.090
instead of yours?

37:23.300 --> 37:24.420
That's what happened.

37:24.420 --> 37:25.650
I lost my shoes.

37:25.650 --> 37:27.650
And a kind guy happened to

37:27.650 --> 37:29.740
throw away a pair of new shoes,
and you found them.

37:30.980 --> 37:32.530
You're pretty good at lying.

37:33.820 --> 37:35.460
A girl in a guy's shoes,

37:35.490 --> 37:36.940
isn't that odd?

37:37.050 --> 37:38.340
Tell me what exactly has happened.

37:39.420 --> 37:40.340
You're back.

37:46.690 --> 37:47.420
Mom,

37:48.300 --> 37:50.300
Qingyu was bullied

37:50.300 --> 37:51.860
at school.

37:52.170 --> 37:54.300
Qiao Beiyu's past

37:54.300 --> 37:55.780
somehow got dug out again.

37:55.900 --> 37:58.900
It's gone viral on the forums.

37:59.090 --> 38:00.130
It's not just her.

38:00.340 --> 38:02.980
I've also been dragged into it
at the sports school.

38:13.610 --> 38:15.900
Qingyu, I was being too nervous
just now.

38:18.170 --> 38:19.940
You've had a tough time at school.

38:20.820 --> 38:22.860
But... Why didn't you tell me?

38:24.340 --> 38:25.210
Ever since we came back
from Nanqiao Village,

38:25.460 --> 38:26.570
you've been looking so glum.

38:26.820 --> 38:28.210
You're quiet.

38:28.860 --> 38:30.460
I can't read your mind,

38:31.490 --> 38:33.210
and I'm busy with the shop all day.

38:33.940 --> 38:35.940
You have to tell me
if anything happens, right?

38:41.420 --> 38:43.210
Qingyu, we went through all the hassle

38:43.260 --> 38:44.570
to get you here to study

38:45.050 --> 38:46.780
so that you can get into
a good university

38:46.780 --> 38:48.170
and have a better future.

38:48.940 --> 38:49.490
Right now,

38:50.460 --> 38:51.610
we have to endure it

38:52.340 --> 38:53.530
and keep a low profile.

38:53.740 --> 38:55.300
There are things we can't explain.

38:55.860 --> 38:57.050
Doing so will only make it worse.

38:58.740 --> 39:00.260
Let the hurtful words go.

39:00.980 --> 39:02.980
They'll fade.

39:04.780 --> 39:05.740
Over time,

39:07.050 --> 39:08.090
people will forget.

39:09.530 --> 39:10.570
I need to go now.

39:12.010 --> 39:13.570
The food is ready in the pot.

39:15.650 --> 39:16.980
I need to head back to the shop.

39:32.980 --> 39:35.420
If I hadn't told the truth earlier,

39:35.650 --> 39:37.420
you'd still be getting scolded.

39:38.820 --> 39:40.210
What did Mom say to you?

39:41.460 --> 39:42.300
Nothing.

39:43.490 --> 39:45.740
She talked to you for quite long.

39:46.420 --> 39:47.570
She's always like this.

39:48.130 --> 39:50.260
She wants me to share
everything with her,

39:50.260 --> 39:51.530
but then she's being so domineering

39:51.530 --> 39:53.210
and makes me do things her way.

39:53.980 --> 39:55.980
She just refuses to listen to me at all.

39:56.460 --> 39:57.690
Maybe adults are all like this.

40:01.570 --> 40:02.610
To be honest,

40:03.380 --> 40:06.260
we don't have to mind those awful words.

40:06.690 --> 40:08.530
Everyone thinks low of Qiao Beiyu

40:08.530 --> 40:09.860
and badmouths her,

40:10.130 --> 40:11.650
but has anyone ever thought about

40:11.780 --> 40:13.900
what she went through before she died?

40:16.340 --> 40:18.090
What did she go through before she died?

40:20.340 --> 40:22.260
The man who caused her miscarriage

40:22.620 --> 40:24.460
must be held accountable.

40:25.420 --> 40:26.860
But even if we find him,

40:26.860 --> 40:28.530
she can't be brought back to life.

40:29.530 --> 40:31.210
Still, we can't let it slide.

40:32.570 --> 40:34.210
Qiao Beiyu was so beautiful,

40:34.650 --> 40:36.900
and she had many boyfriends.

40:37.130 --> 40:38.740
I saw several myself.

40:39.610 --> 40:41.900
Who would be her boyfriend

40:42.610 --> 40:43.780
in Nanqiao Village?

40:48.740 --> 40:49.420
Yuck.

40:50.260 --> 40:52.130
These candles are from years ago.

41:37.620 --> 41:41.310
♪Perhaps♪

41:41.820 --> 41:47.520
♪The more we care,
the more careful we become♪

41:48.660 --> 41:54.060
♪Counting the distance
that separates us♪

41:55.060 --> 42:00.620
♪A single step,
and we'd be closer still♪

42:06.290 --> 42:09.960
♪In the future♪

42:10.420 --> 42:16.140
♪Time will reveal this secret♪

42:17.640 --> 42:22.710
♪Waiting is a silent promise♪

42:23.960 --> 42:29.120
♪That never expires♪

42:32.720 --> 42:37.190
♪Turns out that what's on my mind♪

42:38.190 --> 42:41.860
♪Is your name♪

42:42.360 --> 42:47.460
♪The only stubbornness in my heart♪

42:48.540 --> 42:51.760
♪At first sight♪

42:52.190 --> 42:55.470
♪The future has been determined♪

42:56.160 --> 43:01.720
♪Dreams began to feel real♪

43:02.820 --> 43:06.360
♪Turns out that what's on your mind♪

43:06.820 --> 43:10.760
♪Is a place♪

43:11.060 --> 43:16.620
♪Where the same story is held dear♪

43:17.290 --> 43:20.660
♪Fortunately, I'm not sensible enough♪

43:20.990 --> 43:24.460
♪Courage wasn't late too♪

43:24.990 --> 43:31.060
♪Only then does time not betray
our acquaintance♪
